quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  52,0,Bismillaahir Rahmaanir Raheem
  52,1,Wat-Toor
  52,2,Wa kitaabim mastoor
  52,3,Fee raqqim manshoor
  52,4,Wal baitil ma'moor
  52,5,Wassaqfil marfoo'
  52,6,Wal bahril masjoor
  52,7,Inna 'azaaba Rabbika lawaaqi'
  52,8,Maa lahoo min daafi'
  52,9,Yawma tamoorus samaaa'u mawraa
  52,10,Wa taseerul jibaalu sairaa
  52,11,Fawailuny yawma 'izil lil mukaazzibeen
  52,12,Allazeena hum fee khawdiny yal'aboon
  52,13,Yawma yuda'-'oona ilaa naari jahannama da'-'aa
  52,14,Haazihin naarul latee kuntum bihaa tukazziboon
  52,15,Afasihrun haazaaaa am antum laa tubsiroon
  52,16,Islawhaa fasbirooo aw laa tasbiroo sawaaa'un 'alaikum innamaa tujzawna maa kuntum ta'maloon
  52,17,Innal muttaqeena fee jannaatinw wa na'eem
  52,18,Faakiheena bimaaa aataahum rabbuhum wa waqaahum rabbuhum 'azaabal jaheem
  52,19,Kuloo washraboo haneee 'am bimaa kuntum ta'maloon
  52,20,Muttaki'eena 'alaa sururim masfoofatinw wa zawwaj naahum bihoorin 'een
  52,21,Wallazeena aamanoo wattaba'at hum zurriyyatuhum bieemaanin alhaqnaa bihim zurriyyatahum wa maaa alatnaahum min 'amalihim min shai'; kullum ri'im bimaa kasaba raheen
  52,22,Wa amdadnaahum bifaa kihatinw wa lahmim mimmaa yashtahoon
  52,23,Yatanaaza'oona feehaa kaasal laa laghwun feehaa wa laa taaseem
  52,24,Wa yatoofu 'alaihim ghilmaanul lahum ka annahum lu'lu'um maknoon
  52,25,Wa aqbala ba'duhum 'alaa ba'diny yatasaaa'aloon
  52,26,Qaalooo innaa kunnaa qablu feee ahlinaa mushfiqeen
  52,27,Famannnal laahu 'alainaa wa waqaanaa 'azaabas samoom
  52,28,Innaa kunnaa min qablu nad'oohu innahoo huwal barrur raheem
  52,29,Fazakkir famaaa anta bini'mati rabbika bikaahininw wa laa majnoon
  52,30,Am yaqooloona shaa'irun natarabbasu bihee raibal manoon
  52,31,Qul tarabbasoo fa innee ma'akum minal mutarabbiseen
  52,32,Am taamuruhum ahlaamuhum bihaazaaa am hum qawmun taaghoon
  52,33,Am yaqooloona taqawwalah; bal laa yu'minoon
  52,34,Falyaatoo bihadeesim misliheee in kaanoo saadiqeen
  52,35,Am khuliqoo min ghairi shai'in am humul khaaliqoon
  52,36,Am khalaqus samaawaati wal ard; bal laa yooqinoon
  52,37,Am'indahum khazaaa'inu rabbika am humul musaitiroon
  52,38,Am lahum sullamuny yastami'oona feehi falyaati mustami'uhum bisultaanim mubeen
  52,39,Am lahul banaatu wa lakumul banoon
  52,40,Am tas'aluhum ajran fahum mim maghramim musqaloon
  52,41,Am 'indahumul ghaibu fahum yaktuboon
  52,42,Am yureedoona kaidan fallazeena kafaroo humul makeedoon
  52,43,Am lahum ilaahun ghairul laa; subhaanal laahi 'ammaa yushrikoon
  52,44,Wa iny yaraw kisfam minas samaaa'i saaqitany yaqooloo sahaabum markoom
  52,45,Fazarhum hatta yulaaqoo yawmahumul lazee feehi yus'aqoon
  52,46,Yawma laa yughnee 'anhum kaidumhum shai'anw wa laa hum yunsaroon
  52,47,Wa inna lillazeena zalamoo 'azaaban doona zalika wa laakinna aksarahum laa ya'lamoon
  52,48,Wasbir lihukmi rabbika fa innaka bi-a'yuninaa wa sabbih bihamdi rabbika heena taqoom
  52,49,Wa minal laili fasabbihhu wa idbaaran nujoom
